-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"--font-weight:theme;\">FAQs \u2013 Answer Engine Optimisation in Kenya<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-8695ec16f832e9 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;\">We\u2019ve answered some of the most common questions Kenyan businesses and marketers ask about AEO. If you\u2019re still unsure whether it\u2019s right for your brand, these insights should help clarify the value and scope.<\/div><\/div>[vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What\u2019s the minimum budget to run a Display campaign?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052221-d2dccac3-2f8e82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"353\" data-end=\"556\">We typically recommend a starting monthly budget of KES 25,000 to KES 50,000, depending on your goals (e.g., awareness vs conversions), the geographic scope, and the competitiveness of your industry.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"804\">While Google Display Ads can operate on even smaller budgets, anything under KES 20,000 often lacks the scale to generate meaningful data or impact. For remarketing-only campaigns, lower budgets can be effective due to the narrower targeting.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Are banner ads effective in Kenya?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052312-795bf34f-889a82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"850\" data-end=\"935\">Yes \u2014 when executed correctly. Display ads are especially effective in Kenya because:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"1274\">\n<li data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"1024\">\n<p data-start=\"939\" data-end=\"1024\">Internet usage is high across mobile and desktop (over 63% penetration, CAK 2023)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1152\">\n<p data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1152\">Users spend significant time on platforms that are part of the Google Display Network (e.g. YouTube, mobile apps, news sites)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1153\" data-end=\"1274\">\n<p data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1274\">Most local businesses still focus heavily on social media or search, meaning less competition for display inventory<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1438\">That said, success depends on proper targeting, creative quality, and frequency controls. Poorly executed campaigns tend to underperform regardless of market.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can I run both Search and Display together?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361191995-ff8a0d69-1fe982d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1493\" data-end=\"1533\">Absolutely. In fact, it\u2019s best practice.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1717\">\n<li data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1632\">\n<p data-start=\"1537\" data-end=\"1632\">Use Search Ads to capture high-intent users actively looking for your products or services.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1633\" data-end=\"1717\">\n<p data-start=\"1635\" data-end=\"1717\">Use Display Ads to build awareness, drive engagement, and retarget warm leads.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1719\" data-end=\"1889\">Our clients who combine the two see higher conversion rates, lower CPAs, and stronger brand recognition. We structure campaigns so they work in tandem \u2014 not in silos.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What\u2019s the difference between Display Ads and Programmatic Ads?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361240947-6ed290f2-a03582d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"2025\">Both serve banner or video ads across websites and apps, but:<\/p>\n<div class=\"_tableContainer_80l1q_1\">\n<div class=\"_tableWrapper_80l1q_14 group flex w-fit flex-col-reverse\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<table class=\"w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)\" data-start=\"2027\" data-end=\"2647\">\n<thead data-start=\"2027\" data-end=\"2130\">\n<tr data-start=\"2027\" data-end=\"2130\">\n<th data-start=\"2027\" data-end=\"2051\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Feature<\/th>\n<th data-start=\"2051\" data-end=\"2089\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Google Display Ads<\/th>\n<th data-start=\"2089\" data-end=\"2130\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Programmatic Ads<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody data-start=\"2236\" data-end=\"2647\">\n<tr data-start=\"2236\" data-end=\"2338\">\n<td data-start=\"2236\" data-end=\"2259\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Platform<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2259\" data-end=\"2297\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Google Display Network (GDN)<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2297\" data-end=\"2338\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Multiple networks (incl. GDN)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"2339\" data-end=\"2441\">\n<td data-start=\"2339\" data-end=\"2362\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Access<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2362\" data-end=\"2400\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Google Ads account<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2400\" data-end=\"2441\" data-col-size=\"sm\">DSP (Demand Side Platform) required<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"2442\" data-end=\"2544\">\n<td data-start=\"2442\" data-end=\"2465\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Targeting<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2465\" data-end=\"2503\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Google audience data<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2503\" data-end=\"2544\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Cross-platform audience data<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"2545\" data-end=\"2647\">\n<td data-start=\"2545\" data-end=\"2568\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Cost<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2568\" data-end=\"2606\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Generally lower setup costs<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"2606\" data-end=\"2647\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Higher setup + platform fees<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div class=\"sticky end-(--thread-content-margin) h-0 self-end select-none\">\n<div class=\"absolute end-0 flex items-end\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p data-start=\"2649\" data-end=\"2849\">For most small to mid-sized businesses in Kenya, Google Display Ads are more accessible and cost-effective. Programmatic is ideal for national brands or agencies managing multiple brands at scale.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can you help with ad creative too?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361291476-30b845c7-304f82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2895\" data-end=\"2944\">Yes. We provide full creative support, including:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2946\" data-end=\"3088\">\n<li data-start=\"2946\" data-end=\"2972\">\n<p data-start=\"2948\" data-end=\"2972\">Static banners (JPG\/PNG)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2973\" data-end=\"2988\">\n<p data-start=\"2975\" data-end=\"2988\">Animated GIFs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2989\" data-end=\"3011\">\n<p data-start=\"2991\" data-end=\"3011\">Responsive HTML5 ads<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3012\" data-end=\"3055\">\n<p data-start=\"3014\" data-end=\"3055\">Short video assets for YouTube or display<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3056\" data-end=\"3088\">\n<p data-start=\"3058\" data-end=\"3088\">Creative testing and refreshes<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3090\" data-end=\"3195\">All ads are designed to match your brand guidelines, campaign objectives, and GDN technical requirements.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][\/vc_tta_accordion][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; type=&#8221;vc_default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;5&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;10&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716548610536{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][vc_single_image image=&#8221;5598&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; lazy_loading=&#8221;true&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row